# Plot the data
ggplot(feedintake, aes(days)) +
  geom_rect(
    data = shaded_ranges,
    aes(xmin = xmin, xmax = xmax, ymin = -Inf, ymax = Inf),
    fill = "lightgray",
    alpha = 0.5,
    inherit.aes = FALSE
  ) +
  geom_line(aes(y = `100KO`, color = "100KO")) +
  geom_point(aes(y = `100KO`, color = "100KO")) +
  geom_line(aes(y = `75KO`, color = "75KO")) +
  geom_point(aes(y = `75KO`, color = "75KO")) +
  geom_line(aes(y = `50KO`, color = "50KO")) +
  geom_point(aes(y = `50KO`, color = "50KO")) +
  geom_line(aes(y = `25KO`, color = "25KO")) +
  geom_point(aes(y = `25KO`, color = "25KO")) +
  geom_line(aes(y = `0KO`, color = "0KO")) +
  geom_point(aes(y = `0KO`, color = "0KO")) +
  scale_color_manual(
    values = c("100KO" = rgb(252, 78, 42, maxColorValue = 255),
               "75KO" = rgb(253, 141, 60, maxColorValue = 255),
               "50KO" = "yellowgreen",
               "25KO" = "forestgreen",
               "0KO" = "darkolivegreen"),
    labels = c("100KO", "75KO", "50KO", "25KO", "0KO")
  ) +
  labs(color = "Diet") +
  theme_classic() +
  ylab("Cumulative feed intake per fish (g)") +
  xlab("Days") +
  ggtitle("Cumulative feed intake per fish over time") +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(0, max(feedintake$days), by = 10))
